MedicationRequestRequestorFamilyNameSearchParameter

Parameter requestor.family:string

Searches for MedicationRequest based on the Practitioner's family name eg) /ws/fhir2/{release}/MedicationRequest?requestor.family={familyName}

ResourceMedicationRequest
Expression(none)
Target ResourcesMedicationRequest
MultiplesThe parameter cannot repeat or have multiple values
